{
  "stem": "20088.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was a-- well, a boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Brooksma, he came one day after we had been there very short.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, well, you know they do house searches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans knew, of course, that Jews had disappeared not come in the concentration camp, but just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they knew the Jews were hiding all over the country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they wanted to find those.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they did quite often-- it was called [DUTCH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "House searches.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At night, they came with big lorries and 10, 12 Nazis jumped out, knocked on doors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And went in and did house searches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, if they found people, they arrested not just the Jews but the families who were hiding them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he came to look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had-- in this-- it was this little part where we were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it was upstairs, a little room and the little bedroom, and there was a bathroom and toilet as well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was a long room with the toilet at the end of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said, what we will do is we'll make a partition so that it will look as if it's just a bathroom, not a toilet.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And with a tiled-- we'll tile it, and we'll make a trapdoor with tiles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if they come, you'll go sit on the toilet and-- it was, of course, quite small.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you'll put this trap door on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they won't know that you are there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they work and they brought all the material.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was a Sunday evening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were nearly finished, and they thought, well, let's finish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's late.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then they said, no, let's finish it completely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then at least we don't have to come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It's done.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
